msgctxt "84_Scared Businesswoman"
msgid "My gosh, was that a yakuza!?"
msgstr "Dios mío, ¿¡eso era un yakuza!?"

msgctxt "96_Confident Businesswoman"
msgid "He must have been. Most likely a pretty powerful one, by the look of things."
msgstr "Debe haberlo sido. Probablemente uno muy poderoso, por lo que parece."

